text: Serik Nyghmetuly Akhmetov (; born 25 June 1958) is a Kazakh politician. He was the 8th Prime Minister of Kazakhstan from 24 September 2012 to 2 April 2014 and served as the Minister of Defense from 2 April to 22 October 2014. ==Other websites== * OnlineZakon.kz Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Kazakhstan
